<DOCNO>WT04-B25-55</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA082-000568-B039-270</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://greenpeace.org:80/~ozone/radiant/3rad.html 193.67.176.1 19970103180541 text/html 6435
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
