<H1>Inventory of Production Plants</H1>
<HR>  
<HR ALIGN=LEFT WIDTH=40%>

<P>
The following inventory lists the known producers of ODS during the years 1986 to
1995.  Last known production capacities are listed, except for plants known to be
closed.  Production capacity does not equal actual production; in industrial countries,
Montreal Protocol regulations have limited the amount of production allowed at many of
these plants considerably below the actual capacities.
</P>
<PRE>
ARGENTINA

CFC + HCFC-22 Production Plant:

     Du Pont (Ducilio)  Closed in late
     1993/early 1994.

