<DOCNO>WT04-B25-82</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA082-000568-B040-46</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://greenpeace.org:80/~ozone/holes/7hole.html 193.67.176.1 19970103180958 text/html 5799
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 03 Jan 1997 18:12:35 GMT
Server: Apache/1.0.0
