</DOCHDR>
 <HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>No Excuses - Commercial Refrigeration</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY>
<IMG HEIGHT=26 WIDTH=100% SRC="excuseh.gif" ALT="Greenpeace - No Excuses">


<H2>2.2 Commercial Refrigeration</H2>
   <HR WIDTH=100%>
  <HR ALIGN=RIGHT WIDTH=30%>
 <P> 
  <IMG HSPACE=5 SRC="pixel.gif">
  Commercial refrigeration in supermarkets, hospitals and other public 
  facilities that service food,  encompasses the use of both chiller 
  cabinets, for temperatures around  0 degrees Centigrade, and cold stores 
  which could go down to -28 degrees Centigrade.  
</P>
<HR WIDTH=80%>
 <P ALIGN=CENTER>
 <A HREF="7excuse.html"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="gpdotbk.gif" ALT="Go Back"></A>
<A HREF="index.html"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="gpdotup.gif" ALT="Index: No Excuses"></A> 
<A HREF="9excuse.html"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="gpdotfd.gif" ALT="Go Forward"></A>
</P>
<HR>
</BODY>
</HTML>
