  Information Paper, OzonAction Information Clearinghouse, OzonAction 
  Programme, July 1994:
   Section 2.2.1, p.4 <A HREF="#r1">[return]</A>
  </P>
  <P>
   <A NAME="f2">**</A> ENDS Report 236, September, 1994, p.28 <A HREF="#r2n3">[return]</A>
  </FONT>
  </P>
