and reviewed this report. In particular, we want to thank Richard Tol and Kees 
Dorland for their precise reading of several drafts.
<P>
We also thank E. van Meijgaard, J. Beersma, A. Klein Tank, A. Buishand and G. 
K&ouml;nnen (Royal Netherlands Meteorological Institute) for the inspiring discussions, 
