<DOCNO>WT04-B25-136</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA082-000568-B041-272</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://greenpeace.org:80/~climate/flood_report/2-2.html 193.67.176.1 19970103182503 text/html 1193
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 03 Jan 1997 18:27:42 GMT
