<DOCNO>WT04-B25-163</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA082-000568-B042-233</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://greenpeace.org:80/~climate/2020/brake.html 193.67.176.1 19970103183124 text/html 2338
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 03 Jan 1997 18:34:03 GMT
