<head>
<title>"Sinking Fast: How Factory Trawlers Are Destroying U.S. Fisheries"</title>
<META Name="description" Content="Greenpeace report documenting the destructive practice of using factory fishing trawlers to catch fish in coastal U.S. waters.">
<META Name="keywords" Content="fisheries trawlers factory Tyson's seafood Seattle fish industry 
bycatch waste Magnuson water fleet Bering Sea Alaska Greenpeace USA environment">
<body background="pix/back1.gif" text="#00 00 00" link="#00 80 00"
vlink="#80 00 00" alink="#FF FF 00" basefont=3>
<img src="pix/sinkhed5.gif" width=565 height=100 ALT="Sinking Fast"><br>
