<td><img src="pix/blue.gif" width=126 height=2></td>
<td valign=top>
<table cellpadding=5 cellspacing=0 border=0>
<tr><td align=right><b><a href="intro.html"><p>Introduction</a></b></td><td><font size=-1>The Global Fishing Crisis</font></td></tr>
<tr><td align=right><b><a href="chapter1.html"><p>Chapter 1</a></b></td><td><font size=-1>The Rise of Factory Trawlers and the Industrialization of Fishing</font></td></tr>
<tr><td align=right><b><a href="chapter2.html"><p>Chapter 2</a></b></td><td><font size=-1>The Distant Water Fishing Nations, Part 1</font></td></tr>
