<image align=right src="../icons/head2.gif" width=350 height=240>

<br clear=all><B><font size=+3>Fish </FONT> - &nbsp;<font size=-1>&nbsp;from <font size=+2>&nbsp;<I>Sargasso </I> </font>&nbsp; by <font size=+2>&nbsp;<I>Marjorie Agosin</FONT>
<font size=+2>
<P>I greet the fish of the sea
<P>respecting their ancient
lineage,
<P>their swift, smooth dances,
<P>their colors that reveal
<P>other colors,
