<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>Sirius on the Wee Bankie - Quicktime movies</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="FC9C9C" TEXT="130036" LINK="D51C27" VLINK="970000" ALINK="E200A9">

<table border=0 width=100% cellpadding=6>
<tr><td valign=top>



<a href="act02.html"><img border=1 ALIGN=right WIDTH=100 HEIGHT=70 src="../thumbs/ns21t.jpg"></a>


<H2>Quicktime Movies of Greenpeace action against industrial fisheries on the Wee Bankie, NorthSea. </H2>

</td></tr>
</table>

<center>
<table border=0 width=80% cellpadding=6>
<tr>
<td  width=50% align=right>
