<DOCNO>WT04-B25-207</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA081-000564-B027-91</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://greenpeace.org:80/~comms/cbio/fodder.html 193.67.176.1 19970103185854 text/html 16079
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 03 Jan 1997 19:01:31 GMT
Server: Apache/1.0.0
