<DOCNO>WT04-B25-211</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA081-000564-B027-132</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://greenpeace.org:80/~comms/cbio/global.html 193.67.176.1 19970103185935 text/html 10723
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 03 Jan 1997 19:02:10 GMT
