<DOCNO>WT04-B25-216</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA081-000564-B027-251</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://greenpeace.org:80/~comms/cbio/case.html 193.67.176.1 19970103190211 text/html 8718
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 03 Jan 1997 19:04:48 GMT
Server: Apache/1.0.0
Content-type: text/html
Content-length: 8547
