<DOCHDR>
http://greenpeace.org:80/~thoml/frst_use.html 193.67.176.1 19970103190323 text/html 13961
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 03 Jan 1997 19:06:00 GMT
Server: Apache/1.0.0
Content-type: text/html
Content-length: 13789
Last-modified: Sun, 16 Jul 1995 22:56:53 GMT
