<head>

<br><head><h4>
Transcript of satellite phone report from Stephanie Mills aboard the Rainbow Warrior (recorded by Reuters)....

</h4></head><body>


 
<P>"They have just come alongside.  They've put this grappling hook on the lower deck.  There is one commando now boarding.

<P>They are dressed in black... there is one coming on board.  They've boarded."

<P>[She says they are carrying gas grenades]

<P>"There's now about six or eight on board.  One is now on the bridge and he's ordering people around.
<P>He's just ordering everybody to stop, to sit down... They are coming to the bridge now.
<P>They are telling the photographer to sit down and stop taking photographs.
<P>They are telling everybody to stand back and they've got cannisters of some sort.  They are shouting through the bridge window."

<P>"...They have pushed our cameraman over.  We can't see anything except the sea and somebody's feet at the moment."  [Note: she was speaking from the radio room below decks]

<P>"... I can see the bridge now.. our first mate is on the bridge... I can see them tapping on the windows through the outside... " [contact broken].
