<head>

<br><head><h4>


Latest....</h4></head><body>
 
<P>

Rainbow Warrior Captain Jon Castle has locked himself up in the crow's nest with a radio and is in contact with the MV Greenpeace.  Meanwhile two of the inflatables have made it into the Moruroa lagoon and two Greenpeace divers are now in the water under the test platform.  MV Greenpeace campaigner Xavier Pastor has told the French military that they cannot go ahead with the test with the divers in the water.  The test, we understand, is imminent. </body></html>


