http://greenpeace.org:80/~comms/rw/cbrief.html 193.67.176.1 19970103195359 text/html 7459
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 03 Jan 1997 19:56:36 GMT
Server: Apache/1.0.0
