<html><P align=right> <a href="rw.html"><image align=right src="srwa.gif" border=0 ></a><P><br><br><br><br><br>
<head><H4>Government and Opposition Statements on the resumption of nuclear testing.
Updated 21th July 1995</H4></head><body>
 
<P><B>Including Statements of Opposition from:</B>
 
<li><A HREF="#Argentina">Argentina</A>
<li><A HREF="#Australia">Australia</A>
<li><A HREF="#Austria">Austria</A>

<li><A HREF="#Belgium">Belgium</A>
<li><A HREF="#Brazil">Brazil</A>

<li><A HREF="#Canada">Canada</A>
<li><A HREF="#Czech Republic">Czech Republic</A>
<li><A HREF="#Chile">Chile</A> 

<li><A HREF="#Denmark">Denmark</a>

<li><A HREF="#Fiji">Fiji</A>
<li><A HREF="#Finland">Finland</A>
