 <P>    After 1985:
. sailed aboard Greenpeace yacht 'Vega' to Moruroa in 1985
. continued as skipper on a number of other Greenpeace ships
including the new Rainbow  Warrior's 1991 voyage to Moruroa lived
in the Marshall Islands for a year 
      Now: 
. age, 41
. based in Palma, Majorca
. professional skipper
. married to former Greenpeace ship's doctor, one child      
