radioactivity at Mihama nuclear power plant (Japan)<BR>
10-1992: Technical failure in pump system at Zaporozhe
nuclear power plant (Ukraine)<BR>
11-1986: Release of 13 tonnes of radioactive carbon
dioxide from Transfynydd nuclear power plant (UK)<BR>
12-1968: A B-52 plane with nuclear bombs on board crashes
near Toronto (Canada)<BR>
13-1960: First French nuclear test<BR>
14-<BR>
