Point Lepreau (Canada)<BR>
21-1976: Accident at Bohunice nuclear power plant
(Slovakia)<BR>
22-1993: High pressure steam accident kills one worker and
injures two others at Fukushima nuclear power plant
(Japan)<BR>
23-1981: Accidental explosion of a Pershing-II missile in
Germany<BR>
24-1972: Accident on board Soviet nuclear-powered
submarine causes vessel to lose all power<BR>
25-1983: Failure of automatic shut-down at Salem nuclear
power plant (USA)<BR>
26-1988: Increased levels of radioactivity at Bohunice
nuclear power plant (Slovakia)<BR>
27-1983: Nuclear powered satellite falls into the Indian
Ocean<BR>
28-1992: Software failure in the control computer at
Embalse nuclear power plant (Argentina)
 
 
